n></p></td><td width=\"355\" style=\"border-top-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-right-width: 1px; padding: 0px 7px;\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 125%;\">包括</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; line-height: 125%;\">GMC</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 125%;\">软件应用、</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; line-height: 125%;\">GMC</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 125%;\">沙盘、</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; line-height: 125%;\">GMC</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 125%;\">大赛</span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td width=\"178\" style=\"border-right-color: windowtext; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-left-color: windowtext; border-right-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-left-width: 1px; border-top-style: none; padding: 0px 7px;\"><p><span style=\";line-height:125%;font-family:宋体\">证券模拟与金融统计分析</span></p></td><td width=\"232\" style=\"border-top-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-right-width: 1px; padding: 0px 7px;\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\";line-height:125%;font-family:宋体\">张晨</span></p></td><td width=\"355\" style=\"border-top-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; border-right-width: 1px; padding: 0px 7px;\"><p><span style=\";line-height:125%;font-family:宋体\">包括证券模拟实验设计、数据更新</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"text-indent:37px;line-height:35px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\">、项目主任绩效管理</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:32px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">根据项目主任